{"tid":614674,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國出台新規限制VPN 外企在華經營成本上升","createTime":"2018-04-02T17:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T13:24:34.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5116153845137aed082523b4009bbe4c1287ceee","tid":614674,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"中國針對旨在避開國內互聯網限制的虛擬專用網絡(VPN)服務採取打擊行動，在華經營的外國公司將由此面臨更多成本和麻煩。按照上周六生效的規定，企業只能使用經中國政府批準的VPN。<br />\nLiza Lin發自上海 / Yoko Kubota發自北京<br />\n2018年4月2日09:00 CST 更新<br />\n中國針對旨在避開國內互聯網限制的虛擬專用網絡(VPN)服務採取打擊行動，在華經營的外國公司將由此面臨更多成本和麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n按照上周六生效的規定，企業只能使用經中國政府批準的VPN。企業組織和諮詢人士認為，VPN規則調整是中國政府收緊網絡空間限制的全面行動的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n上海美國商會(American Chamber of Commerce)和諮詢公司化險諮詢(Control Risks)近期發布報告稱，調整前的VPN規則&ldquo;極為模糊，很少有或根本沒有執法行動&rdquo;。報告還稱，中國將禁止&ldquo;一切未經政府批准、未在政府登記或接受政府評估的事項&rdquo;。<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CT-BGH-20180402083037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2FCT-BGH-20180402083037&d=Ww3No2Xf%2BZLTpZb%2F7euX4QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=754f547c\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CT-BGH-20180402083037</a>"},{"pid":"0537d6f6321932eb2a689d688a48c41e9847a0ce","tid":614674,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T23:36:15.000Z","msg":"智者建橋<br />\n愚者建牆<br />\n<br />\n支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f7e00f750c34175585f7a4400b234a55a4eefd","tid":614674,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0537d6f6321932eb2a689d688a48c41e9847a0ce","tid":614674,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T23:36:15.000Z","msg":"智者建橋<br />\n愚者建牆<br />\n<br />\n支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}